<p><a name="Siegfried" id="Siegfried"></a></p>
<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Der_Ring_des_Nibelungen&amp;action=edit&amp;section=9" title="Edit section: Siegfried">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Siegfried</span></h3>
<p>Wagner's score of <i>Siegfried</i> requires all the instruments of <i>Das Rheingold</i>, except for the following:</p>
<ul>
<li>In the percussion instruments, the bass drum is omitted.</li>
<li>In the percussion instruments, all 18 anvils are omitted.</li>
<li>In the percussion instruments, the thunder machine is omitted.</li>
<li>In the percussion instruments, one glockenspiel is added.</li>
<li>In the plucked strings, one of the harps is omitted, so only six harps are used.</li>
</ul>
<p>Thus, Wagner's original score of <i>Siegfried</i> requires a total of 119 instruments.<sup id="cite_ref-34" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-34" title=""><span>[</span>35<span>]</span></a></sup></p>
