<li id="cite_note-magee-0"><b><a href="#cite_ref-magee_0-0" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="book" id="CITEREFMagee.2C_Bryan2001">Magee, Bryan (2001). <i>The <a href="/wiki/Tristan_chord" title="Tristan chord">Tristan Chord</a>: Wagner and Philosophy</i>. Clearwater, Fla: Metropolitan Books. pp.&#160;109. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/080507189X" class="internal">ISBN 0-8050-7189-X</a>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=The+%5B%5BTristan+chord%7CTristan+Chord%5D%5D%3A+Wagner+and+Philosophy&amp;rft.aulast=Magee%2C+Bryan&amp;rft.au=Magee%2C+Bryan&amp;rft.date=2001&amp;rft.pages=pp.%26nbsp%3B109&amp;rft.place=Clearwater%2C+Fla&amp;rft.pub=Metropolitan+Books&amp;rft.isbn=0-8050-7189-X&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Der_Ring_des_Nibelungen"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
